<p style="Heading 1"><c props="lang:en-GB"></c>1.1.1 Changelog</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Christian Biesinger</p>
<p style="Normal">Documentation for Star Office importer.</p>
<p style="Normal">Improvements to Star Office importer, including reading metadata.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix GDict plugin to build even when libgdict isn't installed.</p>
<p style="Normal">AbiWord can import metadata from other formats.</p>
<p style="Normal">Build fixes.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on UT_Map.</p>
<p style="Normal">Framework for Hancom importer, and basic text import.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Scott Bingman</p>
<p style="Normal">Build instructions update.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Jonas Bjrk</p>
<p style="Normal">QNX dialogs for revisions and metadata.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 3396.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Jesus Corrius</p>
<p style="Normal">Catalan localisation fix.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Jeremy Davis</p>
<p style="Normal">AbiPaint plugin menu fix.</p>
<p style="Normal">AbiMagick plugin fixes for Win32.</p>
<p style="Normal">Patch to make libole2 work on Win32.</p>
<p style="Normal">popt fix on Win32.</p>
<p style="Normal">Commandline processing work on Win32.</p>
<p style="Normal">Win32 build system fix.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on the Win32 version of the dictionary hash downloader.</p>
<p style="Normal">Consolidated XP code for dictionary hash downloader.</p>
<p style="Normal">Win32 inclusion of ut_endian.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Andrew Dunbar</p>
<p style="Normal">New version of the world.abw file which tests language and script support.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Hubert Figuiere</p>
<p style="Normal">MacOS X port work, including new dialogs.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed some breakage on Win32.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Frank Franklin</p>
<p style="Normal">Version number fix.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixes to the dictionary hash downloader.</p>
<p style="Normal">Build system fixes.</p>
<p style="Normal">Clean up Aiksaurus CVS tree.</p>
<p style="Normal">Ditch non-libxml2 html stuff.</p>
<p style="Normal">Updated svenska.hash from external maintainers.</p>
<p style="Normal">Something to do with libtoolize that he didn't seem to like much.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added UT_UCS2_mbtowc &amp; UT_UCS4_mbtowc.</p>
<p style="Normal">Next-gen build system for plug-ins.</p>
<p style="Normal">Disabled freetranslation plugin, as it needs to be rewritten.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on the Cocoa (MacOS X) build system.</p>
<p style="Normal">Build fix for ImageMagick plugin (thanks to Hub).</p>
<p style="Normal">Added build option to build against glib2.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed libxml2 build problems.</p>
<p style="Normal">Changed build system to verify that pspell exists before building against it.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added a -spec option to the plugin build system. This has something to do with getting sensible rpms, I think.</p>
<p style="Normal">Make *BSD builds default to peer libiconv.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added ABI_OPT_GNOME=2 option to build system.</p>
<p style="Normal">Simplified autoconf build system and fixed it to support glib2.</p>
<p style="Normal">Some fixes to wv build system.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Tomas Frydrych</p>
<p style="Normal">Changed Abi to use a 32-bit internal Unicode representation.</p>
<p style="Normal">Pango related code.</p>
<p style="Normal">Removed non-bidirectional layout code.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added pango to the tree.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added config.h.msvc to popt.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed ut_xml_expat.cpp.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed fribidi related out of bounds writes in xap_Strings.cpp  and ev_Toolbar_Labels.cpp.</p>
<p style="Normal">Updated to latest fribidi.</p>
<p style="Normal">Changed UT_Mbtowc to UT_UCS4_mbtowc.</p>
<p style="Normal">Internal changes to handle encoding of large character sets properly.</p>
<p style="Normal">Committed some fixes to fribidi.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a build failure on Linux.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a crashing bug in bidirectional code.</p>
<p style="Normal">Changed the way foreground color works, to integrate with revisions code.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a bug with UT_wctomb.</p>
<p style="Normal">Split fv_View into three files, because it was over 12000 lines long.</p>
<p style="Normal">Did some code voodoo to lookupProperties.</p>
<p style="Normal">Document-level properties for language and dominant direction.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on revision tracking, so that changes made to a document are visible, and associated with the person who made them.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on UI for using revision tracking.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added hidden text formatting.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 3351</p>
