<p style="Normal">Minor abiwidget fixes.</p>
<p style="Normal">Support for Bonobo/Zoomable:1.0 interface.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added document properties/metadata, such as author and subject.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added dialog to set document metadata.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bare beginnings of the port to GTK2. Abi still builds against GTK 1.2, and still doesn't build against GTK2.</p>
<p style="Normal">Advertised the PropertyBag information to the system, which should make Abi fully embeddable.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix Nautilus viewer.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix Abi so that it doesn't assume that LANG is set.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix to let us build against the latest versions of libxml2.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fix in revisions to prevent a segfault on typing.</p>
<p style="Normal">Transferring UT_ASSERT to use proper macros, and thus be more informative.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a build problem on Red Hat.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes in revisions to allow building on Linux.</p>
<p style="Normal">Beginnings of a system to let you press f1 when a dialog is open, and automatically get the help.</p>
<p style="Normal">Removed lots of wchar_t's, and cleaned up dead bits of code.</p>
<p style="Normal">Make pspell work again.</p>
<p style="Normal">Revision UI for unix.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added File &gt; Save Template.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a problem on Win32.</p>
