<p style="Normal">Fix to AP_convert.</p>
<p style="Normal">Converted to use libpopt for command-line parsing on GTK and GNOME builds.</p>
<p style="Normal">Made AP_Args use AP_App.</p>
<p style="Normal">UCS4Char fixes for MacOS X.</p>
<p style="Normal">Timer implementation for MacOS X.</p>
<p style="Normal">popt implementation for MacOS X.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on key input for MacOS X. (Yes, the ability to type and have it appear in the program. The MacOS X port is some way behind other platforms.)</p>
<p style="Normal">Other MacOS X work.</p>
<p style="Normal">Build cleanup.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix to ut_mutex.</p>
<p style="Normal">Improvements to code for commandline options.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixes to LaTeX exporter.</p>
<p style="Normal">Privatised fp_Run.cpp.</p>
<p style="Normal">Removed redundant warnings.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed fields to respect the formatting of surrounding text (so that a field inserted into italicised text is itself italicised).</p>
<p style="Normal">Refactored some insertSpan code.</p>
<p style="Normal">Committed a big ugly piece of code to reduce property leakage.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed the bug that made text following an endnote reference appear in endnote reference style rather than normal.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed crashes on undoing endnote insertion.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 3215.</p>
